You have pretty hands.

01:01:36.737 --> 01:01:37.977
- Are they?
- Yes.

01:01:39.207 --> 01:01:40.777
Noona, your hands are pretty too.

01:01:42.217 --> 01:01:44.117
- Sorry?
- Your hands are pretty too.

01:01:46.147 --> 01:01:47.517
(Shy)

01:01:50.987 --> 01:01:55.297
Mu Jin called me
"Noona" for the first time.

01:01:55.497 --> 01:01:57.057
At the time, I...

01:01:58.797 --> 01:02:00.643
It kind of felt real for the first time.

01:02:00.667 --> 01:02:01.644
Really?

01:02:01.668 --> 01:02:05.307
Until now, I was kind of immersed
in the emotions from before.

01:02:05.807 --> 01:02:10.253
I was just happy and having fun.

01:02:10.277 --> 01:02:12.247
But earlier, - She
must've been taken aback.

01:02:12.377 --> 01:02:14.453
I had so many thoughts
in my head about Mu Jin.

01:02:14.477 --> 01:02:15.493
This is huge.

01:02:15.517 --> 01:02:19.087
Because I have a younger brother
who's much younger than me.

01:02:20.487 --> 01:02:23.487
In that case... I am attracted to Mu Jin,

01:02:24.257 --> 01:02:26.863
but will we really be okay
once we learn about our ages?

01:02:26.887 --> 01:02:29.927
I still have that thought.

01:02:30.797 --> 01:02:32.403
We can just think about dating,

01:02:32.427 --> 01:02:35.273
but I'm usually the type who
considers marriage as I date.

01:02:35.297 --> 01:02:37.073
- She's very careful and serious.
- So,

01:02:37.097 --> 01:02:40.283
later on, when our
ages are finally revealed,

01:02:40.307 --> 01:02:42.277
will we be okay? I'm
curious about that myself.

01:02:44.737 --> 01:02:48.817
(Bon Hee has a rush of emotions
upon hearing the word "Noona.")

01:02:49.577 --> 01:02:50.847
- Let's try them on.
- Okay.

01:02:54.747 --> 01:02:55.933
(Slipping it on)

01:02:55.957 --> 01:02:57.157
- It's just...
- Perfect.

01:02:57.387 --> 01:02:58.557
It fits perfectly for me too.

01:03:01.387 --> 01:03:04.257
They're really pretty. I like them.

01:03:04.597 --> 01:03:06.767
- Do you like them?
- Yes, they're so pretty.

01:03:06.927 --> 01:03:09.197
- We should take a photo.
- Okay.

01:03:10.367 --> 01:03:12.237
Crossed? Like this?

01:03:14.067 --> 01:03:16.013
We both have pretty hands.

01:03:16.037 --> 01:03:17.283
Yes, they're pretty.

01:03:17.307 --> 01:03:19.207
- Like this?
- In 1, 2, 3.

01:03:21.447 --> 01:03:22.947
- They look good on us.
